headline: Here’s What TD Cowen Thinks About Leidos Holdings (LDOS)
summary: ​Leidos Holdings, Inc. (NYSE:LDOS) is one of the Best Cybersecurity Stocks to Buy in 2026. On January 16, Gautam Khanna from TD Cowen reiterated a Hold rating on the stock and lowered the price target from $210 to $190.
